00:31:53.640 --> 00:31:56.430
understand exactly what Google
goes through when we try to

00:31:56.430 --> 00:31:59.450
get our data to you,
and vice versa.

00:31:59.450 --> 00:32:01.520
So thanks for coming over and
meeting with us today, Fitz,

00:32:01.520 --> 00:32:02.480
